text: Kim Young-mi (; born 18 August 1960) is a South Korean sport shooter who competed in the 1984 Summer Olympics and in the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female sport shooters Category:ISSF rifle shooters Category:Olympic shooters of South Korea Category:Shooters at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Asian Games medalists in shooting Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for South Korea Category:Shooters at the 1986 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 1986 Asian Games
